<body>
<h1> welcome <%= @name %>! are you ready to play rock, paper scissors? </h1>

<h2> when you're ready to play, choose one option below. remember - rock beats scissors, scissors beat paper and paper beats rock! </h2>

<p1> you'll play against the computer, the one with the most points after 3 turns is the winner! </p1>


<form action="/rock" method="get">
  <button class=button type="submit">ROCK</button>
</form>
<form action="/paper" method="get">
  <button class=button type="submit">PAPER</button>
</form>

<form action="/scissors" method="get">
  <button class=button type="submit">SCISSORS</button>
</form>
</body>

</html>
